* Query Logs\nwith KQL
** Access
***_ Azure portal
***_ Log Analytics workspace
***_ Logs sidebar item
** Basic Query Structure
***_ Table name
***_ | where (filter)
***_ | project (select columns)
***_ | order by
***_ | take (limit)
** Investigate Job Failures
***_ where Response contains "error"
***_ | summarize by OperationName
***_ | bin(TimeGenerated, 1h)
***_ Spot systemic issues
** Track Cluster Usage
***_ summarize by OperationName
***_ Count event types
** Monitor Unity Catalog
***_ Filter getTable / selectFromTable
***_ Track data access
** Query Tips
***_ Save to Query explorer
***_ Organize in folders
***_ Share with team
